message.body: You don't happen to have Will or Steph's number do you?
Hey, sorry. Meant to text back that it was all good. I was trying to pick up Will's laptop but ended up finding him. On another note, would you be around tomorrow if I drop off those lights?

Hey, wasn't sure if you were available earlier today, but I was rushing to get ready. If you want to drop by for those lights, Zac should be around, or I might be able to drop them off Thurs, otherwise I'll be around at the end of June.
It's cool I'll get me when u get back. Have a good trip
Sounds good. See you on the flippety floppety.
